  "topic": "Nonlinear functions / quadratics",
  "source": "sat8",
  "stem": "The function f is defined by f(x) = 8x³ + 4. What is the value of f(2) ?",
  "choices": [
    "68"
  ],
  "answer": "68",
  "explanation": "Substitute x = 2: f(2) = 8(2)³ + 4 = 8(8) + 4 = 64 + 4 = 68."
}
